{"tid":1382132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貴州山泥傾瀉增至36亡","createTime":"2019-07-29T11:47:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T12:10:55.000Z","uid":53026,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1e8ae2aa64161c26eba53735393b22163d930583","tid":1382132,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:47:37.000Z","msg":"貴州山泥傾瀉增至36亡<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】貴州六盤水市水城縣雞場鎮坪地村23日晚發生山泥傾瀉。截至昨天早上11時30分已導致36人遇難，11人送醫救治，仍有15人失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n上周受連日暴雨影響，貴州發生兩宗山泥傾瀉，其中據官方日前估算，水城縣的山泥傾瀉量達200多萬立方米，落差約500米，當地23戶共77人受災，27棟房屋中有21棟被掩埋。<br />\n<br />\n中新網報道，經多種方式核查，受災區域共有戶籍人口22戶77人，外來探親訪友、務工🇨🇳人員🇨🇳8人，共計85人，其中已取得聯繫的在外🇨🇳人員🇨🇳23人。貴州官方通報指，救援隊伍截至28日11時許搜救出36名遇難者，救出11名傷者並送院，15人失蹤。現場消防、武警、安能以及社會其他組織與🇨🇳人員🇨🇳的搜救工作仍在繼續。"},{"pid":"85cd93760cb9a41a61877497b9c7253371d3d98f","tid":1382132,"uid":274658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:49:28.000Z","msg":"一講完就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc9387a2fc29f6df00cf1d81ca03146a3f46f2d6","tid":1382132,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:49:37.000Z","msg":"放心，頂多死多1個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a763347eb88435c93ce1aa331029782ec108d0","tid":1382132,"uid":35113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:51:22.000Z","msg":"次次都死36人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d193bc42f0e434c478b20d578e11f109fa15f0c","tid":1382132,"uid":214534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:51:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好！</span>"},{"pid":"34d3ed390cb72789e545d26767ce91f9ce1dc64c","tid":1382132,"uid":214534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:52:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Yeah</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2060c57ec9643f22f87ecb5715eccad435a844a5","tid":1382132,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:55:16.000Z","msg":"不如話中囯唔會死人"},{"pid":"45854a1701969461570057338207099482a9456d","tid":1382132,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:02:15.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2b7e18b6263141382d0becc53710bd76697f6c","tid":1382132,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8a763347eb88435c93ce1aa331029782ec108d0","tid":1382132,"uid":35113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:51:22.000Z","msg":"次次都死36人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:08:47.000Z","msg":"只要一開頭少過35人死就得。先失縱後死亡都唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6326b840f875ea5b29e3edfb23c6e5f306438f0","tid":1382132,"uid":7296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:09:43.000Z","msg":"多難興邦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1511aa9105e344b876c85ed0562db0adeeb8a7f4","tid":1382132,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:10:55.000Z","msg":"又係呢個magic number"}]}